Tie/CSV_File version 0.01
=========================

SYNOPSIS

  use Tie::CSV_File;

  tie my @data, 'Tie::File', 'xyz.dat';
  
  print "Data in 3rd line, 5th column: ", $data[2][4];
  
  untie @data;
  
  [NOT YET IMPLEMENTED]
  $data[1][3] = 4;
  $data[-1][-1] = "last column in last line";
  push @data, [qw/Jan Feb Mar/];
  delete $data[3][2];

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Text::CSV_XS
    Tie::File

The test routine requires additional these other modules and libraries:

    Test::Exception
    Test::More
    File::Temp

